Michael Mccurdy BiographyAward-winning artist Michael McCurdy has illustrated more than 170 books for adults and children. His books often explore America's past, bringing to life its history and traditions. He lives with his wife, Deborah, on a farm in western Massachusetts.Michael McCurdy currently resides in Great Barrington Springfield, in the state of Massachusetts. 
Biography
Award-winning artist Michael McCurdy has illustrated more than 170 books for adults and children. His books often explore America's past, bringing to life its history and traditions. He lives with his wife, Deborah, on a farm in western Massachusetts.Michael McCurdy currently resides in Great Barrington Springfield, in the state of Massachusetts. 
