About McCurdy Construction & Remodel - Phoenix, AZ
























































 
 








ABOUT MICHAEL MCCURDY
In late 2007, Michael McCurdy decided to bring his years of construction experience together to form McCurdy Construction in Arizona. Mike likes to work closely with his clients to come up with the best remodeling solution for each customers individual needs. This may sound quite obvious but in Mike’s experience, each project should be considered its own individual situation which has its own problems to be solved and hurdles to overcome.
What has worked on one project in the past may not work on another. Communication with his clients, attention to detail and excellent workmanship standards all come together to bring any project, big or small to completion on time and within budget. That is what this company is all about.
Mike will make a point to listen to your desires and needs for your home. After your initial needs are addressed, he will design the perfect solution for your remodeling project. McCurdy Construction specializes in Residential and Small Commercial Remodeling in Phoenix Arizona.
Mike likes to say that whatever construction service your home or business needs he can take care of it for you. Your project is our obsession. We will build your project as if it was our own.
Every member of our staff is hand-picked for their expertise in each part of your home renovation process. So whether you have a specific blueprint in mind or would like to take advantage of our design consultations, we have the expertise and training to ensure that your renovation project is completed, on time and within your budget.
Product selections can sometimes seem a bit overwhelming and frustrating at times. This is when the interior designer can become the single greatest asset to the completion of your renovation project. Their expertise in the design selection and space planning will save you an immense amount of stress and headaches. Having a designer who already works with a renovation company is extremely beneficial. Communication increases with a designer and things run smoother. This is what helps make the entire process much easier for you. That is our #1 goal.

   

CONTACT Phone Number: (480) 247-3113
Email: info@mccurdyremodel.com
One of our representatives will respond back to you within 24-48 hours.

 Licensed-Bonded-Insured
#240967/ #249487


















